data.title: Joint Briefing Paper
data.meta_description: Joint briefing paper - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The following briefing paper has been produced in the lead-up to the 12th European Union (EU)-Laos human rights dialogue, scheduled to be held on 12 July 2023 in Vientiane. It contains a summary of key political and human rights developments since the previous dialogue, which was held on 13 July 2022 in Brussels.
